{"tid":1850171,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「直播」修補布拉格連儂牆","createTime":"2020-01-29T11:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T22:38:05.000Z","uid":101548,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ae208dc611f0609fa632f2b70b1e4594caf873","tid":1850171,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"大家係香港是否好愁，唔知大家口罩存量仲有幾多？<br />\n去左歐洲旅行的我們係一個口罩都買唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠14億蝗蟲爭奪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到亞洲面孔入藥房已經西面同我地講no mask<br />\n<br />\n琴日灰灰地去左布拉格連儂牆影相，<br />\n發覺有連豬仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多stand with hong kong/願榮光歸香港的字，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzXjSpx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzXjSpx.jpg&h=8b2d4f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7YOLKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7YOLKz.jpg&h=d844a21d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/29/194458_5ba3a7d12f47744b7d046e1cea0dc1cc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F29%2F194458_5ba3a7d12f47744b7d046e1cea0dc1cc.jpeg&h=2e13ff65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但發現部分應該比蝗蟲塗污。<br />\n<br />\n所以同朋友傾左陣，<br />\n決定係布拉格最後一天，<br />\n自行接左呢個支線任務。"},{"pid":"17336c864961230338f37ef01b14cbef4ed1743b","tid":1850171,"uid":101548,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YwCjSqN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYwCjSqN.png&h=1a936379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地有的材料有<br />\n臨時係超市買的<br />\nmarker3支，<br />\n同塗改液2支，<br />\n完。<br />\n<br />\n等緊車出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943b9b353835b056a03697e3490bfbdf9c2acd8a","tid":1850171,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislik